document_data.name: Eilean's Maztica Delights
document_data.mainbody: '''Eilean's Maztica Delights''' was a shop located in [[Waterdeep]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: The building was two storeys tall.
document_data.Location: Eilean's Maztica Delights was located in the north section of the [[Waterdeep/Castle Ward|Castle Ward]] on the southeast corner of the intersection of [[Trader's Way (Waterdeep)|Trader's Way]] and [[Sul Street]] bordering the north side of the [[Market (Waterdeep)|Market]].
document_data.Activities: The shop specialized in exotic goods from distant [[Maztica]].
